  navigator.vibrate(10) // light tap
  navigator.vibrate([30, 100, 30]) // error pattern
}
```

## Component Structure

### Glass Card (Performance Optimized)
```css
.glass-card {
  @apply bg-white/95 border border-gray-200/30;
  /* NO backdrop-filter untuk cards */
}

.glass-navbar {
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px); /* HANYA untuk navbar */
}
```

### Modal Size Classes
`modal-xs`, `modal-sm`, `modal-md`, `modal-lg`, `modal-xl`, `modal-full`

## Performance Rules
1. Gunakan `will-change: transform` hanya pada elemen yang akan di-animate
2. Prefer `transform` dan `opacity` untuk animasi (GPU-accelerated)
3. Maksimal 1 `backdrop-filter` visible per viewport (navbar saja)
4. Stagger delay maksimal 0.05s antar item
5. Duration entrance animations: 0.2s - 0.3s
6. Hindari nested Motion components yang berlebihan

## File Organization
- Animations: `src/composables/useMotion.js`
- Global styles: `src/style.css` (minimal, structure only)
- NO `<style>` blocks in Vue files
